				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/2014/09/26/the-old-evidence-problem/?like_comment=624&#038;_wpnonce=38e5d4a57e&#038;replytocom=593#respond' data-commentid="593" data-postid="291" data-belowelement="div-comment-593" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to AR+'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
